lead_paragraph: Borussia Dortmund forward Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang delivered a four-goal apology for his midweek disciplinary suspension as Borussia Dortmund crushed Hamburg SV 5-2 on Saturday to earn their first win in five games.

headline.print_headline: Dortmund's Aubameyang Apologises With Four-Goal Display
headline.main: Dortmund's Aubameyang Apologises With Four-Goal Display
